Once you have installed MobiCheck on your mobile device, you will be able to deposit all your checks using the mobile device.

The MobiCheck application will activate the rear camera on your mobile device and guide you through the next steps. Point the camera at the front face of the check and the application will provide hints on how to best position the camera to capture an optimal image. Once the optimal position has been obtained the application will snap the picture automatically. You will be asked to repeat this process to snap a picture of the back of the check as well.
